/i/Q9CxEen.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQ9CxEen.png&h=bad11dda&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n64%表示頗反對或非常反對中央政府繞過香港立法會，為香港訂立國安法；頗支持或非常支持的有24.3%。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/pg5Z3Gp.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fpg5Z3Gp.png&h=3230d154&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n調查亦訪問受訪者，是否同意香港特區政府有責任處理危害國家安全的行為和活動，表示頗同意或非常同意有責任的達52.3%，不同意的有20.2%，相信反映市民認為呢啲嘢應該自己做。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bRcUSz3.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbRcUSz3.png&h=468f9a78&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n以上可以供大家參考，未來點打民意戰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-01T03:01:14.000Z","msg":"認為就得架喇咩？？？？<br />\n睇事實再講啦<br />\n文宣用多啲力啦"},{"pid":"eb848a20bd646f0910decd4cf0f788cf18828f94","tid":2045670,"uid":128430,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-01T03:02:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bZzstak.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbZzstak.png&h=e6c3f79a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n同場加映<br />\n<br />\n就中央政府現時在香港落實一國兩制的做法，41.4%受訪者給予0分，即「完全唔滿意」，較對上一輪民調（2020年3月19日至27日）同樣給予0分的33.4%，多出百分之八，亦是七輪民調以來，最多人表達「完全唔滿意」的一次，較去年5月第一輪民調22.5%給予0分，高出近19%。"},{"pid":"adb3cf12d80580962574417a66f2f50e29a0c962","tid":2045670,"uid":128430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-01T03:03:19.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c0ecf20e39894419891188e83cb962859fdf0ae7","tid":2045670,"uid":128430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-01T03:03:34.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"588fea5afebae55ac7b0546a6b1a88374267e3aa","tid":2045670,"uid":128430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-01T03:03:45.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"3d5c33e718b5b9fef6fd6d87e8542388ca453dc5","tid":2045670,"uid":264529,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-01T03:03:51.000Z",